::Surgital::

Surgital put one arm out and Alpha Dolphy's shots hit it and went "ting ting
ting!".  Surgital was hit by the energy blast, and stumbled back a bit, but
still had plenty of energy left to destroy stuff.

"The combined power and INTELLIGENCE of the Bodicons can't be beat!"
Surgital said.

Surgital reached down and attempted to grab Alpha and crush her to death,
and at the same time he shot a large energon net at Ice.
